title: Ep45: Online Dating Woes and CosPlay
itunes:title: Ep45: Online Dating Woes and CosPlay
description:
The duo have shared their ups and downs on online dating and decide to dig deeper into what apps are out there to meet people as well as go discuss some Dating App don'ts when it comes to your profile. Is your profile keeping you from finding someone?? Kink of the Week this week is Cosplay and Furries.
